{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitor\/onChanged(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitor","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitor\/FileMonitorProtocol-Implementations"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onChanged"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14FileMonitorRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"FileMonitorRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO7FileRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileRef","text":"FileRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FileRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO7FileRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"text":"FileMonitorEvent","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileMonitorEvent","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO16FileMonitorEventa"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}]}],"name":"flags"},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal handler to call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"changed"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"watchMoves"},{"type":"text","text":" on a directory monitor, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the information is available (and if supported by the backend),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"eventType","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" may be "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"renamed"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"movedIn"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"code":"movedOut","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In all cases ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"file"},{"type":"text","text":" will be a child of the monitored directory.  For"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"renames, "},{"code":"file","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be the old name and ","type":"text"},{"code":"otherFile","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is the new"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"name.  For “moved in” events, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"file"},{"type":"text","text":" is the name of the file that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"appeared and "},{"code":"otherFile","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is the old name that it was moved from (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"another directory).  For “moved out” events, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"file"},{"type":"text","text":" is the name of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the file that used to be in this directory and ","type":"text"},{"code":"otherFile","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"name of the file at its new location."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It makes sense to treat "},{"code":"movedIn","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"equivalent to ","type":"text"},{"code":"created","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"movedOut"},{"type":"text","text":" as equivalent to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"deleted"},{"type":"text","text":", with extra information."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"renamed"},{"type":"text","text":" is equivalent to a delete\/create"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"pair.  This is exactly how the events will be reported in the case"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"watchMoves"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is not in use."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If using the deprecated flag "},{"code":"sendMoved","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"eventType"},{"text":" is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"moved","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"file","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be set to a ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/File"},{"text":" containing the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"old path, and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"otherFile"},{"type":"text","text":" will be set to a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/File","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" containing the new path."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In all the other cases, "},{"code":"otherFile","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NULL"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"code":"changed","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" signal","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/filemonitor\/onchanged(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Emitted when "},{"code":"file","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has been changed.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14FileMonitorRefV","text":"FileMonitorRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO7FileRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"FileRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FileRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO7FileRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"text":"FileMonitorEvent","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO16FileMonitorEventa"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"extendedModule":"GIO","title":"onChanged(flags:handler:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:3GIO19Fi